title: [The Drunken D'Wharf, Tavern]
description: The interior is dimly lit by iron sconces and the walls lined with wooden beams, darkened from years of smoke and soot from a central hearth.  Shelves sag beneath an impressive collection of earthenware jugs, glass bottles, and wooden casks behind a bar crafted from a massive slab of salt-stained oak.  In the corner, a copper still affixed with a drakar plate gleams in the torchlight, its coils twisting over open flames.
room.location: Drunken D'Wharf, inside the island town of Mist Harbor
